text: Ðis is þes landes imare þus uten þinsald.
Arest on land scorhlinc to chiselburne.
Þannen anlang streames þannen up of streame.
On anne hlinchesheaved þanen be suþe Scaftesbury on þane hlinc.
Upward of dy castele to burnstowe þanen on anne linkesheaved.
On anne herepaþ westward over herepaþ.
Þanen on anne crundel to burstowe on anne cnap on anne Ierðlonde Northward þanen.
Of herepaðe on heandene beorg on deuelisc of dune.
On anne furch on anne stan castel.
On land scarlinc an sex made eres be frome be deuelisc made.
